name: Exquisite Corpse Part 10
description:
This is the last part of Exquisite Browser Corpse Project. Please download either Mac or Windows version of part 10 here. 

Instruction of Play: 

W, A, S, D  --- walk forward, left, backward, right

Hold SHIFT +  W, A, S, D --- run forward, left, backward, right

SPACE --- jump

Hold LEFT MOUSE --- zoom in
